text: I attend with my husband on Sundays at 5pm. This is contemporary service with Tamil n English speaking Pastors. Good worship, good sermon n beautiful songs sang by the music team or recorded. We feel blessed n anointed. You will feel the presence of God when worshipping. This is our Church n we love our Church. Do come n join us. There are all ages attending this Sunday service.
A place to worship. Please join with us for Sunday service every morning until afternoon.
You can find God's Love here!
